DOMAIN,amap-aos-info-nogw.amap.com,REJECT,extended-matching
DOMAIN,free-aos-cdn-image.amap.com,REJECT,extended-matching
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,v.smtcdns.com,REJECT,extended-matching

[Map Local]
